text.jpText: 声なき声 不可思議
text.enText: With just a silent voice, Bewildering

text.jpText: そのとき風 揺らめき
text.enText: And at that time the wind, Was wavering

text.jpText: もがいていた背中を押す
text.enText: That gentle push you gave my troubled back

text.jpText: 超えたい壁 gravity
text.enText: That wall I want to pass, is Gravity

text.jpText: そのとき羽 煌めき
text.enText: At that moment my wings, Began to gleam

text.jpText: もう過負荷は次元変換transforming
text.enText: With a dimensional change that will overload, transforming

text.jpText: 誰も見たことのない景色へ
text.enText: To that world with that never seen before scenery

text.jpText: 何も視界にいない世界へ
text.enText: To that empty world with near zero visibility

text.jpText: 限界超えた異次元 on the road
text.enText: To that dimension with limits surpassed, on the road

text.jpText: 選び 加速して行こう別のリアルへ
text.enText: Then as we accelerate to that chosen other reality

text.jpText: 誰も遮ることなく
text.enText: Where there is nobody who can interrupt

text.jpText: 何も恐れるものない進化へ
text.enText: To an evolution where there is nothing to fear

text.jpText: 標識の無い領域の中へ
text.enText: Off to that hidden domain with no signs within

text.jpText: 移行 不可能 可能に変えて
text.enText: Where impossible can be changed to the possible

text.jpText: Go 目の前の世界線を追い越して
text.enText: Go, Before your eyes, There's a horizon to surpass

text.jpText: 見えない光に導かれ ベクトルを変えて行け
text.enText: An invisible guiding Light that leads me forward, Unceasingly It alters my vector

text.jpText: 果てない瞬間 生命(いのち)ごとレベル上げて
text.enText: At the end of Each moment our Existence levels up

text.jpText: 真っ直ぐに
text.enText: Looking straight ahead

text.jpText: さあ 走れ奇跡
text.enText: Look, a Running Miracle

text.jpText: 声なき声 轟き
text.enText: With just a silent voice, It reaches me

text.jpText: 彼方の天(そら) 閃き
text.enText: Way up beyond the sky, Just a glimmer

text.jpText: あの魂 私を押す
text.enText: That spirit pushes me gently forward

text.jpText: 超えてた壁 その瞬間(とき)
text.enText: That wall I made it past, at that time

text.jpText: 数多のほら 響めき
text.enText: How it created a big commotion

text.jpText: もう新たな宇宙 未知なるゴールへ
text.enText: Once more to another Unknown universe, With a goal ahead
